     <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">
      Storing the master files on a trusted
                        location, is a good way to prevent having to rescan an image when
                        requirements change over time (due to new research needs or improved
                        technology which sets higher expectations) or when better post processing
                        methods become available.
     </desc>
